# Match Prediction and Analysis

This is a Football Match Prediction App built using Node.js and Express for the backend, with a focus on providing users with predictions based on recent match data, team standings, and betting odds. The application integrates with the Football-Data API for match data and The Odds API for betting odds, enabling users to make informed predictions about upcoming football matches.

## Features

- Fetch upcoming matches based on user-selected competitions.
- Generate match predictions using a rule-based algorithm that considers team form, head-to-head results, and current standings.
- Retrieve live betting odds from various bookmakers.
- User-friendly API endpoints for seamless interaction.

## Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- Axios (for API requests)
- Football-Data API
- The Odds API

